  "content_id": "4c32934e-a97f-4b36-9320-99d1b987ba69",
  "description": "Record the details of candidates who have completed a Driver Certificate of Professional Competence (CPC) periodic training course",
  "details": {
    "department_analytics_profile": "",
    "external_related_links": [

    ],
    "introductory_paragraph": "<p>Record the details of candidates who have completed a Driver Certificate of Professional Competence (<abbr title=\"Certificate of Professional Competence\">CPC</abbr>) periodic training course. You must be an approved training centre.</p>\n\n",
    "more_information": "<p>You’ll need your:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>user ID</li>\n  <li>password</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Read the <a href=\"/government/publications/guide-to-recording-driver-cpc-periodic-training/guide-to-recording-driver-cpc-periodic-training\">guide to recording Driver <abbr title=\"Certificate of Professional Competence\">CPC</abbr> periodic training</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"giving-another-person-access\">Giving another person access</h2>\n\n<p>You can register another person to use the Driver <abbr title=\"Certificate of Professional Competence\">CPC</abbr> training database if you need them to enter training records. They won’t need to register with the Government Gateway.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"paying-to-record-training\">Paying to record training</h2>\n\n<p>You have to pay to record training details. The fee is £1.25 per driver, per hour of training.</p>\n\n<p>You can pay in 2 ways:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>by debit or credit card</li>\n  <li>by debit from a pre-funded account</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p><a href=\"/use-a-dsa-pre-funded-account\">Setting up a pre-funded account</a> lets you deposit funds with the Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency (DVSA) in advance and pay the fee by debiting the amount directly from your account.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"help-recording-training\">Help recording training</h2>\n\n<p>Contact <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency\">DVSA</abbr> to get help recording training you provide.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>DVSA Driver CPC</strong>\\<br>\n<a href=\"mailto:cpcre@dvsa.gov.uk\">cpcre@dvsa.gov.uk</a><br>\nTelephone: 0300 123 7721<br>\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 5pm<br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n",
    "start_button_text": "Start now",
    "transaction_start_link": "https://driver-services.dvsa.gov.uk/cpctrain",
